# Rasm Rhino Bridge

**Refs**: `tools/rhino-bridge/README.md`, `tools/rhino-bridge/AGENTS.md`, root `AGENTS.md` § LIVE_RHINO_BRIDGE.

## Invoke ONLY when static gates cannot answer

| Need | Command |
|------|---------|
| Library runtime scenarios | `bash scripts/rhino.sh verify <path-or-glob>` |
| Project diagnostics | `bash scripts/rhino.sh bridge check <project.csproj>` |
| Source build proof (no scenario) | `bridge check <source.cs>` → exit 3 = unsupported, not failure |
| Pre-native-edit health | `bash scripts/rhino.sh bridge doctor` |
| RhinoWIP API truth | `bash scripts/rhino.sh api doctor\|path\|xml\|types\|decompile` |

## Do NOT invoke for

- xUnit/CsCheck specs (use `scripts/test.sh`)
- Analyzer/format failures (`check-cs.sh check`)
- Rhino settings/template automation (owned by plugin `LoadTime.AtStartup`)

## Scenario kit

- `Rasm.TestKit.Scenarios` staged automatically — `using Rasm.TestKit.Scenarios;`
- Output: JSON evidence + PNG under `.artifacts/rhino/verify/`
- Host: `/Applications/RhinoWIP.app` (override via `RHINO_WIP_APP_PATH`)

## Bridge change ladder

See serial commands in `tools/rhino-bridge/AGENTS.md` — `bash -n`, shellcheck, `--self-test`, `bridge build`, `check-cs.sh check`, `bridge doctor`, sample verify.
